creator: Michele Lynch
title: Twin Flame Transformation - How to Stop Pushing Your Twin Flame Away
dc:creator: Michele Lynch
content:
Episode 4:  In this episode, Michele talks about how to stop pushing away and/or repelling your Twin Flame.  She discusses how to dance with the negative/positive energies and how to use the sweet love of your Twin Flame to your advantage.  This is powerful and transformative information that could benefit all Twin Flames.  

www.michelelynchhealing.com

Listener Support:  https://anchor.fm/michele-lynch/support
